reviewText: THIS IS A GREAT VIDEO WITH LOT OF INFORMATION ON THE TRAINS.  THE PEOPLE NEED TO KNOW ABOUT THIS.
Excellent video on train travel and scenery.
Great train video for all train lovers!
Our son loves trains.  He got this for Christmas. He is age 12 and really enjoyed them.
This is  a great history lesson for the entire family. There is lots of details about the steam locomotive from delux trains to work trains and adventure is included.
